                            <comment id="13206301" author="dvryaboy" created="Sat, 11 Feb 2012 23:34:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Why -j? I was thinking we could use properties for that:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;pig -Dpig.progress.listener=com.foo.PigListenerImpl -Dpig.progress.listener.args=&quot;foo,bar&quot; -f my_script.pig&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
